    • hasNeighbor

      public boolean hasNeighbor(String p_neighborCountryName)
      The function checks if a given country name is a neighbor of the current country.
      Parameters:
      p_neighborCountryName - The parameter p_neighborCountryName is a String that represents the name of a neighbor country.
      Returns:
      The method is returning a boolean value. It returns true if the given neighbor country name is found in the list of neighbor countries, and false otherwise.
